overview: Puerto Rican salsa sensation Tito Rojas hits Las Vegas with this energetic performance featuring crowd-pleasers such as "Ran-Kan-Kan" and "El Amor Que Tu Me Das" that'll make you want to get up and dance. With a guest appearance by Roberto Roena, the sizzling show also includes "Tormenta de Amor," "Porque Este Amor," "Me Tienes Que Recordar," "Por Mujeres Como Tu" and more.
title: Tito Rojas: Autenticamente En Vivo
